"At last, the deadly forces brought by Gwiti launched their invasion against Wesnoth. As the shadows of his rule terrorize the Kingdom and its people, they turn to the elven enchantress Elynia for their last breath of hope. Will the Light or the Darkness be the one that stands in the end? There was no one who knew, except only one.\n"
"\n"
"(Intermediate level, 6 scenarios.)"
